        <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Reinforcing Immigration Status for Credit Knowledge Act or the RISK Act</strong></p><p>This bill allows a creditor to refuse to extend credit to a non-U.S. national (<em>alien</em> under federal law) who does not have lawful status under U.S. immigration laws.</p><!--tinycomments|2.1|data:application/json;base64,-->]]></text>
      </summary>
